{"type":"message","id":"1d374a03","parentId":"4b75f445","timestamp":"2026-05-13T12:48:07.074Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The process completed successfully with exit code 0. Let me now summarize the results and send them back to the main session.\n\nKey findings:\n1. **打资源** - Completed successfully. Built Android bundles for SoloPackage version 1.1.058. Consuming time: ~132.7s\n2. **上传CDN** - Completed, but with a minor 404 error from `DownloadCDNFile` (likely checking if a remote file exists - not a fatal error). Consuming time: ~1.5s\n3. **本地测试环境** - Set up at D:/cdn_solo/update/Android/Test1/1.0.41\n4. Process exited with code 0 - clean exit\n\nThe 404 error appears to be the pipeline checking for an existing CDN config file that doesn't exist yet (first deployment to this version), and then proceeding to create the local test environment. Since the process exited cleanly, this is a non-fatal issue.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"热更流水线执行完毕，结果如下：\n\n**✅ 流水线完成 (Exit Code: 0)**\n\n**流水线步骤:**\n\n| 步骤 | 耗时 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ① 打资源 (AssetBundle) | 132.7s | ✅ 完成 — 构建成功 SoloPackage 1.1.058 |\n| ② 上传CDN | 1.5s | ✅ 完成 (本地测试环境已就绪) |\n\n**产物信息:**\n- **版本号:** SoloPackage 1.1.058\n- **平台:** Android Test1\n- **本地测试环境:** `D:\\cdn_solo\\update\\Android\\Test1\\1.0.41`\n\n**⚠️ 注意:**\n- CDN 上传步骤有一个 404 警告 (DownloadCDNFile 下载远程文件时返回 404)，可能是检测远端文件是否存在时的正常行为，非致命错误\n- 流水线已成功在本地创建好 CDN 测试目录结构\n\n可以通知测试服更新完毕了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":697,"output":434,"cacheRead":22784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23915,"cost":{"input":0.00009758000000000001,"output":0.00012152,"cacheRead":0.000637952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0008570520000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778676481062,"responseId":"4fb86834-1981-4831-b6ef-4f281c738b6c"}}
